{"tid":1543310,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【制裁無恥學校，請幫手廣傳】","createTime":"2019-09-05T06:43:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T08:45:49.000Z","uid":220434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4837e653ea2854ff8381a49fd0c7499d02e40773","tid":1543310,"uid":220434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:43:59.000Z","msg":"【制裁無恥學校，請幫手廣傳】<br />\n<br />\n每年9月15前後既上課日，教育局會派人去每間中學到headcount數返學人數。學校會好緊張，尤其初中班級。萬一當日唔夠學生返學，到時教育局會再揀一日，再落校數多一次返學人數。只要學校嚮果兩日返唔夠人，又咁岩家長唔記得交家長信/醫生紙請假，學校就會面臨縮班，cut教師職員，兼且殺校既危機。<br />\n<br />\n通常學校會叫老師千丁萬足啲學生某日一定要返學，咁教育局就多數係果一日到校。<br />\n<br />\n橫掂有啲學校都有違道德人性，9月依啲日子又咁易病，你不仁我不義<br />\n<br />\n#做過中學AdmissionTeam<br />\n#校長副校真係會好撚緊張"},{"pid":"c630a354bc582aa76cbd2864a5ff06ae573dec17","tid":1543310,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:44:10.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1sNZBDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1sNZBDb.jpg&h=ace5c24e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KM7Lwx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8KM7Lwx.jpg&h=5719ebc4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SoyFk4T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSoyFk4T.jpg&h=2bffae59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SsV05wz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSsV05wz.jpg&h=d54e941c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EUH604U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEUH604U.jpg&h=74590733&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f19f191194d50f4dbdb52b089ad4894565e5b27","tid":1543310,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:45:15.000Z","msg":"各地區連儂牆要人，文宣大量要大人<br />\n解釋清楚！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全民抗爭，長久戰、拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗<br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制支持「邪惡」「無良」的商店，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪、減少淘寶<br />\n2. 安全情況下跳閘，免費搭港鐵<br />\n3. 夜晚十點咆哮！！！<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一個post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit)<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MKC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=3f711e8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n<br />\n5. 不要說推，試著將呢段訊息copy and paste嚟推post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 每星期做孝子，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 每星期去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股、少掂中港股票<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.05"},{"pid":"66f97663ed8dfbe4c4c67b7576ca373756507523","tid":1543310,"uid":220434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:49:16.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"06a3328fec468adc31c8ccdd8290a04c2dae64cb","tid":1543310,"uid":57542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:51:44.000Z","msg":"依家討論區俾人帶住風向走<br />\n真正有心post唔會有人覆<br />\n<br />\n如果獨立調查委員會話你知&quot;無高官需要問責&quot;你係咪要接受呀？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1441577\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1441577</a>"},{"pid":"102ce6863ce21cfc13f067f95bb1fb8f087e8e59","tid":1543310,"uid":249705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:52:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">下星期一 9月9 大專罷課集會</span></span><br />\n<br />\n作為大專生<br />\n今次開學罷課搞到咁柒<br />\n完全俾中學生比下去<br />\n知道大家好慚愧 好想付出更多<br />\n<br />\n短時間內嘅主題<br />\n係要美國國會通過香港人權法案<br />\n既然7號有塞機場 8號有美國領事館<br />\n點解我哋大專生<br />\n唔襯中學生9號一週一罷<br />\n一齊搞多次罷課集會<br />\n有聲勢浩大既民意表態<br />\n既可以團聚學界<br />\n又為之後嘅三罷打強心針<br />\n<br />\n7號8號9號 一連三日嘅大型示威集會<br />\n就可以show到民意支持<br />\n俾美國國會順利表決通過條人權法<br />\n<br />\n香港就快死啦<br />\n一齊撐住好唔好<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">洗版洗到有組織搞9月9罷課為止</span></span>"},{"pid":"884cde42d3734c7d60e88c8b7ccde146e648d100","tid":1543310,"uid":220434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:57:57.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"20f20cc61ec4951f6e7273acb19e5567a2da6cb4","tid":1543310,"uid":220434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:02:50.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"0ede482a6c60193788c65b697859b48d7579480d","tid":1543310,"uid":220434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:19:11.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"105fcc4e768b2cf08591c0586816978f4dce18cb","tid":1543310,"uid":220434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:26:29.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"d8127e0ea6ae616ea62a19abd83b45cb6ee013fc","tid":1543310,"uid":220434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T05:12:08.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"3a9af0dc896a3ee59f1b8f3b540533cf33daf5b6","tid":1543310,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:04:55.000Z","msg":"[澄清]國難五金課金問題&mdash;照舊課！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih